      "description": "Hemolysis index predictions from the CFD model were compared against published power-law hemolysis correlations drawn from peer-reviewed literature (Giersiepen, Zhang, and Heuser-Opitz models). The literature corpus was reviewed for consistency with the model's predicted scalar stress exposure, and agreement within ±18% was noted across the five operating points. This evidence synthesis is considered complementary to experimental benchmarks and supports the adequacy of the hemolysis sub-model.",
